	Fully covered subdomains:

		- autodiscover
		- blog
		- login
		- webmail


	Mixed content:

		- Images, on blog from:

			- blog *
			- s3.amazonaws.com via wiki.developerforce.com *
			- blogs.developerforce.com *
			- wiki.developerforce.com *

